+     *  <li>if an {@link Option} does <b>NOT</b> exist <b>AND</b>
+     *  <code>stopAtNonOption</code> <b>IS NOT</b> set then add that
+     *  character prepended with "<b>-</b>".</li>
+     * </ul>
